Package com.flipkart.constant

Class FlipFitConstants

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.constant.FlipFitConstants
public class FlipFitConstants extends Object
The FlipFitConstants class contains a collection of constant SQL queries used throughout the FlipFit application. These constants are used for interacting with the database to perform CRUD operations on various entities like FlipFitAdmin, FlipFitGymCentre, FlipFitGymOwner, FlipFitSlot, FlipFitBooking, FlipFitCustomer, and FlipFitUser.

This class centralizes all SQL query strings so that they can be reused throughout the application, ensuring consistency and reducing the risk of SQL errors.
